Cali waa kan ugu horeeyay ee da'dyarta ka mid ah oo qaata diinta [[Islaam|islaamka]], [[Sunni|Ahlu sunaha]] agtooda waa [[Khaliif|Khaliifkii Afaraad]] ee [[Khulafo al-Raashidiinta]]; sidoo kale dadka raacsan [[Shiicada]] waxay u aqoonsan yihiin [[Imaam]]kii kowaad iyo kan xaqa u leh ee ku xiga [[Nebi Muxamed]]. 

Cali wuxuu la wareegay khilaafada ka dib markii [[Cusmaan bin Caffan|Cusmaan bin Cafaan]] la dilay 35H/656, wuxuuna haayay ilaa 40H/661, mudadii uu xilka haayay waxey ku sifeesneyd xasilooni la'aan, fitnadii ka dhalatay dilka khaliifka sadexaad [[Cusmaan bin Cafaan]] ayaa umada kala qeybisay waxaana dhacay dagaalo u dhaxeeya muslimiinta dhexdooda.
= Abtirsiinta =
Waa '''Cali''' bin Abii daalib bin cabdi mudalib bin haashim bin cabdi manaaf bin qusayyi bin kilaab bin mura bin kacab bin lu'yyi bin gaalib bin fihir bin maalik bin nadar bin kinaana bin khuzeyma bin mudrika bin ilyaas bin mudar bin nazaar bin macad bin cadnaan.

Hooyadii faaduma binti Asad bin haashim bin cabdi manaaf bin qusayyi bin kilaab.

Hooyadii iyo aabihiis waa ilmo adeero wuxuu sidaas ku ahaa iska dhal [[Banuu Haashim|banuu haashim]].

